        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Local Public Health And Safety Protection Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Justice to make grants to states that allow local governments to impose firearms laws that are more restrictive than state firearms laws. </p> <p>A state that receives a grant must award subgrants to localities to help implement the more restrictive firearms laws. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
